import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

x = np.linspace(0, 2 * np.pi, 100)
y = np.sin(x)

plt.plot(x, y)
plt.xlabel(r'$x$')
plt.ylabel(r'$\sin(x)$')
